<L>__{interior tent day}
<A>__{the postman and ford.}
<C>__{the postman}
<D>__{president starkey? minneapolis? ford knows what to do?}
<C>__{ford}
<D>__{i thought you were dead.}
<C>__{the postman}
<D>__{so? i'm not making the connection. what's all this then?}
<C>__{ford}
<D>__{i lied. i told people you were in contact with me.}
<C>__{the postman}
<D>__{why?}
<C>__{ford}
<D>__{because i didn't want it to end.}
<C>__{the postman}
<D>__{i don't know how long i can stay, ford. president starkey will send word one day and i will have to move on. understand?}
<C>__{ford}
<D>__{sure. but you'll stay till he sends word? right?}
<A>__{the postman can't answer, just turns and walks out of the tent.}
